        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1960-03-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-02-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="[Unnumbered document following Document 710 (#34)]" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d710a-34">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>—In a letter to <persName corresp="#p_BJF1">Byrnes</persName> dated July 20 (<ref target="#d734">document No. 734</ref>, <hi rend="italic">post</hi>)
                        <persName corresp="#p_GAA1">Gromyko</persName> referred to “our conversation
                    this morning”, at which the question of trusteeship was discussed. No minutes of
                    this conversation have been found.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
